# Auto-Injection üíâ

Laravel automatically resolves Eloquent models defined in route or controller action signatures.

<!-- FULL_CODE_START
// Route Definition
Route::get('/users/{user}', function (User $user) {
    return $user->email;
});
FULL_CODE_END -->

Laravel finds the User with ID matching `{user}`.

# Not just IDs üîë

Bind by other columns (e.g., username/slug).

<!-- FULL_CODE_START
Route::get('/posts/{post:slug}', function (Post $post) {
    return $post;
});
FULL_CODE_END -->
